# GitHub Actions

## Commands GIT

```bash
#adding all files
git add -A
#create new branch
git checkout -b develop
#change branch
git checkout master
```

## Secrets

```bash
gpg --symmetric --cipher-algo AES256 secret.jso #1234
```

